{
  "stem": "1338.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what I was saying is that I was very much alert of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as I could read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I read-- by the age of 10, 11, by that time, I read normal literature.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember that, in that sense, I was very well educated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, at the age of 12, I saw this performance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it impressed me very much, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was aware of literature, whether it was foreign or Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I read voraciously, and so I-- and papers, as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were always on the table.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was something always available to read.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the radio was on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I would certainly listen, and read, and be very much aware of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I knew from the very beginning of rise of Nazism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Coupled to an anti-Semitism of the country where I lived, it certainly made me aware of all of these things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By '35, '36, we are starting getting physical evidence, expulsion of Polish-born Jews from Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some of them wound up in my class-- kids from Germany, one or two, who would show up because they were-- '37, '38.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, starting with the Anschluss, with Austria, and everything else, it was always there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was always, with the news, I was interested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I wanted-- and I read a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I even thought my interpretation, at that time, I thought-- and I'm not so sure I want to change my mind, although I should-- is that I think that I had a better understanding of the times than my father or my uncle, who I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My uncle, in 1939, with the storm troopers, were marching in the street already, taking over Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
